description: This table `McpcPSCellNrFreqRelProfile` stores parameters for Multi-connectivity Power Control (M-CPC) related to Physical Cell ID and frequency relationships within a radio access network, for each cell at a specific time.  Columns include timestamp (`dateTime`), location (`Area_Name`), cell identifier (`CellId`, `Id2`), various IDs (`Id3`, `Id4`), data type and version information (`vsDataType`, `vsDataFormatVersion`), and profile parameters (`McpcPSCellNrFreqRelProfile.mcpcPSCellNrFreqRelProfileId`, `McpcPSCellNrFreqRelProfile.userLabel`, `McpcPSCellNrFreqRelProfile.reservedBy`).
